Utterance: Hi! Welcome back! How have you been since our last session?

That’s great to hear! How was the time with your family?

That sounds lovely! Did you notice any changes in how you felt after spending time with them?
I felt a lot happier afterward. It reminded me of the good times we share.
That’s wonderful! It’s important to nourish those relationships. Have you been able to apply any of the coping strategies we discussed?

That’s fantastic progress! How has that been going for you?
It feels good to have a routine, even if I haven’t heard back from many places yet.
